author: jmcnally
msg: switched from using a custom pool implementation based on pool code in stratum
to use a standard implementation from commons-pool.  The pool in commons is
actually a better fit except that it does not allow per group limits on pooled
objects.  Pretty confident this was not a highly used feature of intake.

author: jmcnally
msg: moved most of the file upload functionality into a commons component.  The
service is a thin wrapper around this component.
